reviewText: Looked like a homemade movie at first, but you must understand that's the way most movies were made during the mid 90's. The special effects are so-so, adult scenes are more toned down compared to the Anime version, but the only thing that really stood out were the tentacles. Its a lot different from the animated version to also let you know. If you seen the anime,watch this. If not read more about this movie before getting it.
Only 2 dvds came in very poor.
This DVD is Good and a lot different then the animation version I recommend this for any one who likes real people playing the roll in a great animation movie.
